{"tid":2325563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖慎入）蛀牙蛀到甩到咁又腫晒！點算！","createTime":"2020-12-14T16:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T15:22:23.000Z","uid":101342,"like":2,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"bdffb1a2ff469aa109ef968b7c0efa1283571d2d","tid":2325563,"uid":101342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T16:16:45.000Z","msg":"蛀牙蛀到大半隻牙甩咗！<br />\n呢兩日突然又痛又腫 然後發現個牙肉腫到變成咁 <br />\n已經預約咗牙醫 但係好驚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n預咗要𠝹開啲牙肉剝牙 <br />\n係咪一定要植牙定係可以搭牙橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B5CxV6D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB5CxV6D.png&h=d5488450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有經驗？<br />\n疫情期間都冇睇過牙醫洗過牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />估唔到一下就變成咁"},{"pid":"356961f872b2bae7d671fbba06a8add0070813a6","tid":2325563,"uid":301989,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"幾耐冇刷牙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9876b56eda3306048412f8d9d41314f7fd969610","tid":2325563,"uid":101342,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"356961f872b2bae7d671fbba06a8add0070813a6","tid":2325563,"uid":301989,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"幾耐冇刷牙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"日日早晚刷牙刷足三分鐘架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99a9f8d4869b44576ab8a6f61678d54426251dc","tid":2325563,"uid":34047,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T16:19:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲啲圖永遠係勁高清<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"741b33d09e52dda2c462a